;a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:863:\"<p>In case you&#8217;ve not seen, <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/news/2015/04/wordpress-4-1-2/\">there was a new critical security release made for WordPress itself a few hours ago</a>.</p>\n\n<p>Most sites should update automatically within 12 hours &#8211; but since the release notes say that the security hole allows complete site take-over by an unauthenticated user (i.e. the worst possible kind of security vulnerability), I&#8217;d recommend updating right away. I&#8217;ve just updated around 100 sites!</p>\n\n<p>David Anderson (founder, lead developer, UpdraftPlus)</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://updraftplus.com/wordpress-4-1-2/\">WordPress 4.1.2</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href=\"http://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:44:\"http://updraftplus.com/wordpress-4-1-2/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"http://updraftplus.com/wordpress-4-1-2/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:48:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a: